Package: elasticIsing
Type: Package
Title: Ising Network Estimation using Elastic Net and k-fold Cross-validation
Version: 0.2
Author: Sacha Epskamp
Maintainer: Sacha Epskamp <mail@sachaepskamp.com>
Description: 
License: GPL-2
Imports: magrittr, glmnet, reshape2, IsingSampler, cvTools, qgraph, akima
Suggests: IsingSampler
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: github.com/SachaEpskamp/IsingSampler
Description: Uses k-fold cross-validation and elastic-net regularization to estimate the
              Ising model on binary data. Produces 3D plots of the cost function as a function
              of the tuning parameter in addition to the optimal network structure.